description: Sent when a card is inserted which is a different type than
what the slot was configured for.

event.Summary: Inserted card type $v3 is not match with slot configuration type $v4

description: The unit number associated with this unit.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventoryUnitNumber

description: An incrimental index of the slot in this unit.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventorySlotNumber

description: Indicates the inserted card type. Will return 0 if the slot is
not full.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventorySlotInsertedCardType

description: Indicates the configured card type. This object may be set with a
corresponding value of agentInventoryCardType if this slot supports
removable cards.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventorySlotConfiguredCardType

description: Sent when a card is inserted which is of a type that is not
supported by the slot.

description: The unit number associated with this unit.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventoryUnitNumber

description: An incrimental index of the slot in this unit.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventorySlotNumber

description: Indicates the inserted card type. Will return 0 if the slot is
not full.
variables.name: NETGEAR-INVENTORY-MIB::agentInventorySlotInsertedCardType

description: The name of the Stack Port for this instance.
